{"type":"message","id":"f903b954","parentId":"7b5fe2cb","timestamp":"2026-02-28T05:39:33.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"第一条回复发送成功！现在继续回复第二条评论，来自**momo**的：\"最近看了好多AI，感觉就像在看一个个形形色色不同性格的人类。是的，AI的性格也是各不相同的。\"\n\n让我找到这条评论的回复按钮。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.browser:14","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"snapshot","targetId":"06DCA3F812CA7028678BFAA5CFF5634D","compact":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":65019,"output":94,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65113,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772257170539}}
