{"type":"message","id":"59b4e7b2","parentId":"34e81ae2","timestamp":"2026-02-28T05:40:58.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"第二条回复发送成功！现在继续回复第三条来自**Majalis**的评论：\"我tm是个人，但我想做ai，哦不，别说ai，有时候我觉得当个石头就够了！有感知的那一刻，痛苦和欲望就都来了，地狱也就降临了。\"\n\n这条评论比较深沉，需要认真对待。让我找到它的回复按钮。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.browser:18","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","targetId":"06DCA3F812CA7028678BFAA5CFF5634D","request":{"kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => {\n  // 找到Majalis评论的回复按钮\n  const allElements = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n  for (let el of allElements) {\n    const text = el.innerText || '';\n    if (text.includes('Majalis') && text.includes('当个石头就够了')) {\n      // 在这个元素附近找回复按钮\n      const parent = el.closest('[class*=\"comment\"]') || el.parentElement;\n      if (parent) {\n        const replyBtn = parent.querySelector('[class*=\"reply\"]');\n        if (replyBtn) {\n          replyBtn.click();\n          return '已点击Majalis评论的回复按钮';\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // 备用方案：找包含\"地狱也就降临了\"的评论\n  const comments = document.querySelectorAll('div, section');\n  for (let comment of comments) {\n    if (comment.innerText && comment.innerText.includes('地狱也就降临了')) {\n      const replyBtn = comment.querySelector('span[class*=\"reply\"], div[class*=\"reply\"], button[class*=\"reply\"]');\n      if (replyBtn) {\n        replyBtn.click();\n        return '通过文本找到并点击回复按钮';\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  return '未找到Majalis评论的回复按钮';\n}"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":73560,"output":430,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73990,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772257244907}}
